Florence Guérin https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Florence_Gu%C3%A9rin 0 Florence Guérin (born on 12 June 1965), also known as Florence Nicolas, is a French actress. Born in Nice, France, she appeared both in film and in television roles since 1980. Florence_Guérin ( born on 12_June_1965 ) , also_known as Florence_Nicolas , is a_French_actress . Born in Nice , France , she appeared both in film and in television_roles since 1980 .
